data.description: Discover suburban bliss in this Sendera Ranch haven, perfectly situated in the highly sought-after Northwest ISD. Proximity to two elementary schools, a middle school, and nearby high schools makes it an ideal family haven. Immerse yourself in a community that exceeds expectations with amenities like parks, pools, walking trails with exercise stations, soccer & baseball fields, a clubhouse, and more. Enjoy upgraded living in this 4 bedroom 2 bath move-in ready beauty, with a recently enhanced dishwasher and chic black blade modern fans in the living and primary bedroom. The washer & dryer are also included! Convenience meets comfort as this property is strategically located in the Alliance Corridor, ensuring easy access to the highway for seamless commuting. Enjoy a short drive to a plethora of entertainment options, diverse restaurants, shopping hubs, and even the airport. Don't miss the opportunity to make this residence your gateway to a vibrant and fulfilling community lifestyle!
